data.name: broomtxt1.Text
data.value: You stood your ground not in pride but utter defeat. You've given up the last bit of hope and accepted the fact that this is the end. After all of the efforts you've made, this is where it all comes to an end. You closed your eyes right as the entity burst through the room. You felt it breathe on your neck and utter something unintelligble. You feel your self slip away. You still aren't sure of what it said. Maybe it said this.
